        CR      R14,R15                                                 00660000
        BH      BADHOT                                                  00670000
        B       GETHOTPN         Get the hot key posn                   00680000
USEITEM LH      R1,ITEMPOSN(R14) Load Offset into MENTXT                00690000
        LA      R15,MENTXT(R1)   Get Address of start of item           00700000
